# How to initialize a project for bazel publication

## Prerequisites

* Clone the empty repository to place the code in. If you do not know the
  repo URL, ask.
* Use the example directory at bazel-go-basic/.bcr to set up the BCR publishing
  * Change what needs to be changed to match to this repository.
* Use the sample workflows from bazel-go-basic/.github/workflows to create similar
  workflows in the new project.
* Create the file LICENSE, fill it out with the Apache 2.0 license text.
* Create the file README.md, add to it at the beginning the links to status icons
  for the workflows defined above.
